"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=world+news+site:kyivindependent.com","Russian semiconductor plant making missile, jet parts hit in Ukrainian attack, military says.","https://kyivindependent.com/massive-drone-attack-hits-russia-semiconductor-plant-reportedly-targeted/","Wed, 21 May 2025 06:47:51 GMT","


