"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=site:entertainmentnow.com","Did Jaelen Johnston Win ‘The Voice' 2025?","https://entertainmentnow.com/the-voice/jaelen-johnston-wins-2025-eliminated-spoilers/","Wed, 21 May 2025 03:14:33 GMT","

So, what happened on the season 27 finale of “The Voice?” Did Jaelen Johnston win or was he eliminated? 

Before we reveal the finale spoilers below: THIS is your SPOILER WARNING. Do not continue reading if you do not want to know if Johnston was eliminated or not. STOP reading if you do not want to know any other winner details from the 2025 finale. 

Now that your spoiler warning is out of the way, let's get on with it. Did Jaelen Johnston win “The Voice” 2025? The answer is … No. He came in second place.

