					Trump Judge Slams Supreme Court, Says Courts Are ‘Not a Denny's'		
	









	
	
		
					Neil Young Stands With Taylor Swift, Bruce Springsteen in Trump's Musician War: ‘You Work for Us'		
	









	
	
		
					Why Trump Is Threatening to Investigate Bruce Springsteen		
	









