	1. “Land of Hope and Dreams (Introduction)”2. “Land of Hope and Dreams (Live)”3. “Long Walk Home (Live)”4. “My City of Ruins (Introduction)”5. “My City of Ruins (Live)”6. “Chimes of Freedom (Live)”

