"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=world+news+site:telegraph.co.uk/us","Trump ambushes South African president with footage of ‘white persecution'","https://www.telegraph.co.uk/us/politics/2025/05/21/trump-ambushes-cyril-ramaphosa-footage-white-persecution/","Wed, 21 May 2025 18:00:00 GMT","


			US president demands explanation from Cyril Ramaphosa for ‘very sad situation'
		

