"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=world+news+site:cnn.com","Russian fighter jet protects ‘shadow fleet' vessel in first such move by Moscow, officials say","https://edition.cnn.com/2025/05/20/europe/russian-fighter-jet-shadow-fleet-intl-cmd","Wed, 21 May 2025 14:51:00 GMT","

