"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=site:coindesk.com","World Network (WLD) News: $135M Fundraising as Orbs Reach U.S. Users","https://www.coindesk.com/tech/2025/05/21/sam-altmans-world-raises-135m-in-token-sale-to-a16z-and-bain-capital-crypto","Wed, 21 May 2025 16:40:17 GMT","

