"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=fifa+world+cup","Club World Cup teams can use exceptional transfer windows to bring players to US","https://www.foxsports.com/articles/cup/club-world-cup-teams-can-use-exceptional-transfer-windows-to-bring-players-to-us","Wed, 21 May 2025 18:04:12 GMT","


