"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=site:hollywoodreporter.com","Joey King in Talks to Join Sandra Bullock, Nicole Kidman in ‘Practical Magic 2' (Exclusive)","https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/joey-king-practical-magic-2-1236223308/","Wed, 21 May 2025 18:40:23 GMT","

